Executive Profile
Simon N. Hudson-Lund  Chief Executive Officer, International Financial Data Services, L.P.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships55--
Background

		Mr. Simon N. Hudson-Lund served as Chief Executive Officer of DST International Holdings at International Financial Data Services Ltd. until June 26, 2017 and its Executive Director until June 26, 2017. Mr. Hudson-Lund served as an Executive Vice President at DST Systems Inc. since March 2014 until February 25, 2017. Mr. Hudson-Lund served as the Chief Executive Officer at DST International Holding since February 21, 2013 until February 25, 2017. He served as Executive ... Chairman of International Financial Data Services at DST Systems Inc until February 25, 2017.  He served as the Chief Executive Officer of International Financial Data Services Ltd. since 2008. Mr. Hudson-Lund served as the Chief Executive Officer of International Financial Data Services (UK) Limited. He serves as Executive Chairman of International Financial Data Services (UK) Ltd. He served as Executive Chairman of International Financial Data Services Ltd. until June 26, 2017. He has served in numerous positions with IFDS U.K., including as the Chief Executive Officer from February 2008 to January 2013, Head of European Transfer Agent Operations from January 2011 to January 2013, Chief Operating Officer from July 2005 to January 2008 and Managing Director Administration Services-Client Finance and Transfer Agent Operations from June 2003 to June 2005. He served positions with Legal and General, where he served as Managing Director and was responsible for providing unit trust administration services to one of the largest fund managers in the UK.Read Full Background




